text: Zhanjiang Sports Centre (Simplified Chinese: 湛江体育中心) is a multi-use stadium in Zhanjiang, China. It is currently used mostly for football matches. The capacity of this stadium is 20,000.湛江市体育中心 - 中国自驾网 ==Footnotes== Category:Football venues in China Category:Sports venues in Guangdong
title: Zhanjiang Sports Centre
